data.Name: Texas Instruments Incorporated
data.Description: Texas Instruments Incorporated (TI), headquartered in Dallas, Texas, is a premier global semiconductor company recognized for its pioneering integrated circuit solutions. As one of the top ten semiconductor firms by sales, TI caters to a wide array of markets such as automotive, industrial, and consumer electronics, thereby playing a crucial role in technological advancements. Committed to innovation and research and development, TI consistently delivers high-performance products that enable customers to create next-generation technologies, solidifying its status as a key player in the dynamic global technology landscape.
data.Address: 12500 TI BOULEVARD, DALLAS, TX, UNITED STATES, 75243
